<div id="pf28" class="pf w0 h8" data-page-no="28"><div class="pc pc28 w0 h8"><div class="t m42f x56 h28 ye6 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON </div><div class="t m430 x27 h51 ye6 ff3 fs2a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5 </div><div class="t m431 x14 h3b ye6 ff7 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">*April 24-30 </div><div class="t m5a x73 h11 y1f9 ff3 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Noble Prince </div><div class="t m432 x1f h11 y1fa ff2 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of </div><div class="t m28 x9d h4b y1fa ff3 fs25 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Peace </div><div class="t m433 x73 he y486 ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SABBATH AFTERNOON </div><div class="t m434 x73 h4c y487 ff1 fs26 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">D</div><div class="t m284 xbc hf y488 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">r. Robert Oppenheimer, who supervised the creation of the </div><div class="t m435 xbc hf y489 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">first atomic bomb, appeared before a Congressional </div><div class="t m373 xbc hf y48a ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Committee [in the United States]. They inquired of him if </div><div class="t m436 x1f hf y54 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there were any defense against the weapon. &apos;Certainly,&apos; the great </div><div class="t ma0 x73 hf y48b ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">physicist replied. </div><div class="t m437 x57 hf y55 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot; &apos;And that is—&apos; </div><div class="t mde x57 hf y48c ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Dr. Oppenheimer looked over the hushed, expectant audience and </div><div class="t m35d x73 hf y27 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">said softly &apos;Peace.&apos; &quot;—Compiled by Paul Lee Tan, </div><div class="t m374 xb3 hf y27 ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Encyclopedia of </div><div class="t mf4 x1f hf y45e ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7,700 Illustrations: Signs of the Times </div><div class="t m187 x5d hf y48d ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rockville, Md.: Assurance </div><div class="t m438 x1f hf y29 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Publishers, 1988), p. 989. </div><div class="t m439 x65 hf y48e ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Peace is an elusive dream for the human race. In 1895 Alfred Nobel, </div><div class="t m43a x1f hf y48f ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the inventor of dynamite, provided for a trust to establish a prize for indi-</div><div class="t m43b x1f hf y490 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">viduals who make an outstanding contribution to peace (Paul Lee Tan, </div><div class="t m18 x73 hf y491 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 988, adapted). In recent years, however, even some winners of the </div><div class="t m234 x73 hf y492 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nobel Peace Prize have been involved in violent conflict. This week </div><div class="t m43c x73 hf y493 ff3 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we&apos;ll read about the only One who can bring true, and everlasting, peace. </div><div class="t m43d xc3 h2d y494 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Week at a Glance: </div><div class="t m27b x63 he y464 ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> Who is the Child prophesied of </div><div class="t m2c9 x73 he y495 ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in Isaiah 9? What kind of deliverance would He bring? How are </div><div class="t m286 x73 he y496 ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">both of Christ&apos;s comings presented in Isaiah 11? </div><div class="t m43e xc3 h2d y497 ff5 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Memory Text: </div><div class="t m2b0 x75 he y498 ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> &quot;For a child has been born for us, a son given to </div><div class="t m43f x73 he y499 ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us; authority rests upon his shoulders; and he is named </div><div class="t m25f x73 he y49a ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Wonderful Counselor, Mighty God, Everlasting Father, Prince of </div><div class="t m440 x73 he y49b ff1 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Peace&quot; </div><div class="t m441 x16 hf y49c ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isaiah 9:6, NRSV). </div><div class="t m442 xc3 hf y49d ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">*Study this week&apos;s lesson to prepare for Sabbath, May I. </div><div class="t m443 x3d hf y10c ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">38 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.0